{"type":null,"faqId":12901,"title":"P7 待机时间短，耗电快，如何解决？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"></span>&nbsp;\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">进入“设置”界面，点击“省电管理”，选择省电模式或关闭后台耗电应用。</span> \n</p>\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=35374\" /> \n<p>\n\t&nbsp;\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>不使用手机时，请关闭屏幕。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>缩短屏幕待机时间。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>降低屏幕亮度。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>降低音量。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">不使用移动网络、蓝牙、</span><span>WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">或</span><span> GPS </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">时，在通知面板中通过快捷开关关闭对应功能。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">华为会在官网发布最新软件版本，请前往</span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"></span><span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/\">http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/</a></span></span><span><span> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">根据型号查询；或通过在线升级进行手机软件版本更新，以获得更好的使用体验。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>若问题依然存在，请联系客服或携带购机发票前往服务网点检修。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=35375\" /></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">进入</span><span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/support/service-center/index.htm\">http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/support/service-center/index.htm</a></span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">查询全国服务网点；</span> <span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">或关注华为终端官方微信平台：华为终端（微信号：</span><span>huaweizhongduan</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">），点击“自助服务</span><span> &gt; </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">服务中心查询”根据屏幕提示查询最近的服务网点。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\